          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Author comment.- There is a possibility that some of",
                "the Nb-91-m measured could have originated via",
                "Mo-92((n,np)+(n,pn))Nb-91-m reactions. The present",
                "cross section value is useful in order to predict",
                "the activity of Nb-91-m formed by irradiation of",
                "natural Mo with reactor neutrons, being the upper",
                "limit for the cross section of Mo-92(n,2n)Mo-91-m.-"
              ]
